import React from "react";

const productsData = [
    {
        id: 1,
        url: '/images/product-1.png',
        name: 'Brown eggs',
        description: 'Raw organic brown eggs in a basket',
        category: 'dairy',
        price: '$10',
        rating: 4.5
    },
    {
        id: 2,
        url: '/images/product-2.png',
        name: 'Sweet fresh stawberry',
        description: 'Sweet fresh stawberry on the wooden table',
        category: 'fruit',
        price: '$20',
        rating: 4.8
    },
    {
        id: 4,
        url: "/images/orange.png",
        name: "Fresh orange",
        description: "Fresh orange juice on a white background",
        category: "fruit",
        price: "$12",
        rating: 4.6
    },
   
    {
        id: 5,
        url: "/images/yogurt.png",
        name: "Strawberry yogurt",
        description: "Strawberry yogurt with granola and berries",
        category: "dairy",
        price: "$5",
        rating: 4.4
    },
    
    {
        id: 6,
        url: "/images/product-veg1.png",
        name: "Organic tomato",
        description: "Organic tomato on a cutting board",
        category: "vegetables",
        price: "$9",
        rating: 4.6
    },
    {
        id: 7,
        url: "/images/product-veg.png",
        name: "Basil",
        description: "Fresh basil leaves on a white background",
        category: "vegetables",
        price: "$4",
        rating: 4.5
    }
];

export default productsData;
